            <title>[PIG-1086] Nested sort by * throw exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1086</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following script fail:&lt;br/&gt;
A = load &apos;1.txt&apos; as (a0, a1, a2);&lt;br/&gt;
B = group A by a0;&lt;br/&gt;
C = foreach B &lt;/p&gt;
{ D = order A by *; generate group, D;}
&lt;p&gt;;&lt;br/&gt;
explain C;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the stack:&lt;br/&gt;
